  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/1a28165ad9f58eeaeeb5eb84f5415f89.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/1a28165ad9f58eeaeeb5eb84f5415f89.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/1a28165ad9f58eeaeeb5eb84f5415f89.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/04badb71bf73a22894df8453984e7c24.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/04badb71bf73a22894df8453984e7c24.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/04badb71bf73a22894df8453984e7c24.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into the neon glow of VNESIS, an adrenaline-fueled homage to the golden era of arcade gaming. It's the '80s reimagined – a 2D side-scrolling adventure wrapped in a 3D world that's as vivid as your most vibrant retro dreams. With over 16 levels, each a labyrinth of nostalgia and challenge, VNESIS doesn't just beckon you to play; it dares you. This is where heart-pounding action meets razor-sharp responsiveness, creating a symphony of arcade excitement. Get ready to blast through a universe that's been crafted with a love for the classics and a passion for the pulse of adventure. VNESIS isn’t just a game; it’s a portal to a time when pixels were king and every jump, shot, and dash was a leap of faith into the spectacular unknown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unleash powerful abilities to dominate the leaderboard - summon allies for that much-needed backup or deploy an impenetrable shield to safeguard your craft. Ready your reflexes, embrace the retro-futuristic vibe, and dive into the action – VNESIS is the ultimate playground for the ace pilot in you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/249cd06b59373f76c098854e5dbbe7b8.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/249cd06b59373f76c098854e5dbbe7b8.webm?t=1720980846\" typ