ctacular unknown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=320 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/c509a43effa4ec94d5eda928ad42b4e2.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/2fc301135303b3aa220af8551062989a.mp4?t=1720980846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unleash powerful abilities to dominate the leaderboard - summon allies for that much-needed backup or deploy an impenetrable shield to safeguard your craft. Ready your reflexes, embrace the retro-futuristic vibe, and dive into the action – VNESIS is the ultimate playground for the ace pilot in you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/249cd06b59373f76c098854e5dbbe7b8.poster.avif?t=1720980846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825290/extras/249cd06b59373f76c098854e5dbbe7b8.webm?t=1720980846\" type=\"vi